{
  "text": "This paper will summarize recent progress in the diagnosis and management of EE and discusses future research directions. Eosinophilic esophagitis was first reported in 1978 [CITATION_1] , but Attwood et al. [CITATION_2] called attention to it as a distinct clinical condition in 1993.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "30769758",
    "[CITATION_2]": "26392879"
